msgid "Relays And Bridges"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/tor.rst:236
msgid ""
"To be a relay, your host must have a public available port. With "
"relaying, you will increase the anonymity of Tor and it is less risky "
"than an exit node."
msgstr ""

